						               													<description>It is your responsibility to find new mineral deposits. This job requires that you be alert with all your senses, that you use the latest technology and that you make good decisions.&amp;#10;Make sure they are economically, socially and environmentally viable!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Mining Exploration your mission is to explore the terrain using your exploration cards. Each terrain must be explored with an appropriate action to earn its points. The player with the highest score at the end of the deck will win the game. The standard version of the game is recommended for people 10 years and older. For players with more experience, it has a section with extensions to the rules which will add more options to the games and an advanced version of the game.&amp;#10;Card game designed for the Explorations Corporate Management of CODELCO (National Copper Corporation of Chile). It was distributed to children in schools in the company influence territory. The objective is to teach the work of mining exploration and basic concepts of geology and mining.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
